00:19:18.769 --> 00:19:22.095
Jack Moore [on video]:
That's the paradox of

00:19:22.095 --> 00:19:22.759
statute.
 

00:19:22.759 --> 00:19:26.368
Ed Bradley [on video]:
 &gt;

00:19:26.368 --> 00:19:28.288
Is it fair to say then,
