00:22:11.108 --> 00:22:13.513
Janet Hathaway [on video]:
 One out of a million they

00:22:13.513 --> 00:22:14.328
say is acceptable.
 

00:22:14.328 --> 00:22:16.160
Ed Bradley [on video]:
 Are they scaring people

00:22:16.160 --> 00:22:16.609
needlessly?
 

00:22:16.609 --> 00:22:18.088
Are they fear mongers?
 

00:22:18.088 --> 00:22:20.404
Jack Moore [on video]:
 Well, there's no question

00:22:20.404 --> 00:22:22.594
that if the risk is greater than
