00:22:25.507 --> 00:22:26.240
disease.
 

00:22:26.240 --> 00:22:28.656
Ed Bradley [on video]:
 You've had a chance to

00:22:28.656 --> 00:22:29.818
look at the NRDC study.
 

00:22:29.818 --> 00:22:33.880
It says children are being
